        <abstract>
            <p>Referring to conversation with Lyell, CD is certain that there was a Miocene glacial period.</p>
            <p>Compliments HWB on the mimetic display at the British Museum. Those at the Museum readily accepted HWB’s "doctrine".</p>
            <p>Was shown genital organs of closely allied Chrysomelidae.</p>
            <p>Albert Günther is candidate for position at Museum.</p>
        </abstract>
